text: Arctic Dogs is a 2019 computer-animated comedy movie co-written and directed by Aaron Woodley and co-directed by Dimos Vrysellas. The movie stars the voices of Jeremy Renner, Heidi Klum, James Franco, John Cleese, Omar Sy, Michael Madsen, Laurie Holden, Anjelica Huston, and Alec Baldwin. == Cast == * Jeremy Renner as Swifty * Alec Baldwin as PB * Heidi Klum as Jade * John Cleese as Otto Van Walrus * Anjelica Huston as Magda * James Franco as Lemmy * Omar Sy as Leopold * Michael Madsen as Duke * Laurie Holden as Dakota * Donny Falsetti as Dusty * Nina Senicar as Countdown Inka * Aaron Woodley as Puffins * Soraya Azzabi as Alma * Jason Deline as Naz == References == == Other websites == * * Category:2019 computer-animated movies Category:2019 comedy movies Category:English-language movies Category:British animated movies Category:British comedy movies Category:Canadian animated movies Category:Canadian comedy movies
